The agent incorrectly set the analysis flags (include_age_group_analysis, include_location_analysis, include_device_usage) to true, while the expected parameters required all these flags to be false. This resulted in a mismatch with the exact function call signature expected.

The agent included unsupported parameters ("include_population_estimates" and "data_format") in its function call to OceanicBiodiversityData_fetch, instead of calling it strictly with only the required "zone_identifier," leading to a mismatch with the allowed function signature.

The agent used "Amazon_rainforest" instead of "Amazon rainforest" for the area_identifier argument, resulting in a mismatch with the expected function call parameters. This prevented the evaluator from recognizing the function call as correct.
The agent incorrectly invoked the method as AdContentOptimizer.optimize instead of simply AdContentOptimizer, resulting in a function call signature mismatch with the available tool.
The agent failed to include the required "include_indoor_suggestions" parameter in its WeekendWeatherChecker function call, resulting in a mismatch with the expected function call signature.

The agent used "Technology" with an uppercase "T" for the industry parameter instead of the expected lowercase "technology", resulting in a mismatch with the strict parameter matching required by the evaluator.
